    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014not a scratch or a smudge in sight! It drives like a dream and the interior still has that fresh, new-car smell. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner super happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
