      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather remains supple with no signs of wear, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history and a drive that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence in its most perfect state.",
