      "description": "Available now is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and retains its factory-spec ZF 6-speed manual gearbox for pure mechanical engagement. The suspension maintains original geometry with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution remains uncompromised. Every aspect of the drivetrain, from the limited-slip M-differential to the cross-drilled rotors, is in peak operational order. This is a rare opportunity for a collector to acquire an analog icon with zero deferred maintenance and impeccable structural integrity.",
